    "name": "Surrounded by Death",
    "steam_appid": 3096210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096210/extras/190cfc925d9a6e649dd8f3a7a2c884cc.avif?t=1734629380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096210/extras_big/190cfc925d9a6e649dd8f3a7a2c884cc.avif?t=1734629380 width=800 height=178 /></span><br>Sidescrolling Castlebuilder. Real-time strategy game.<br><br>We lived peacefully in our lands. We cultivated the land and enjoyed peace and quiet. However, such idyll could not last forever. Death came for us. Imperim tried to defend us but lost battle after battle. Now we're left alone <br>now we are Surrounded by Death.<br><br><strong><u>Rule the castle</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Create houses, clinics, try to please the inhabitants.<br></li><li> Create an economy, assign workers to work, distribute food rations to your subjects and trade<br></li><li> Watch out for various events such as drought, plague and much more<br></li><li> Hire a magician and collect magic points<br></li><li> Conduct an extensive research campaign to develop your city<br></li><li> Capture or destroy abandoned cities</li></ul><br><br><strong><u>Fight and defend your subjects</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Create a mighty army<br></li><li> Fight against countless hordes<br></li><li> Prepare for the arrival of a large horde, secure your subjects<br></li><li> Kill the enemies surrounding you to make more space<br></li><li> Destroy all the portals around you so that death has no way to get to you</li></ul>",
